description:
For an international project in Chennai, we are urgently looking for a full remote Senior RPA Developer with \\+8 years of development experience in Front\\-End development and strong knowledge of RPA (Automation Anywhere), finance and accounting systems/ functionalities and integration methodologies.










 We are looking for a motivated contractor. Candidates need to be fluent in English.










**Tasks and responsibilities:** 



* Work on end\\-to\\-end RPA lifecycle, from requirements gathering to deployment and maintenance;
* Develop and Implement necessary objects and BOTs needed for automating the use cases;
* Collaborating with business analysts and developers to design and implement RPA solutions;
* Identifying and prioritizing RPA opportunities within the Finance function and other relevant areas;
* Ensuring the scalability and security of RPA solutions;
* Collaborate with technical teams to ensure RPA solutions are designed and implemented according to best practices and security standards;
* Participate in technical reviews and testing of RPA solutions;
* Monitor and track technical risks and issues related to RPA implementations;
* Assist in the creation of technical documentation for RPA solutions;
* Ensure proper handoff of RPA solutions to support and maintenance teams;









**Profile:** 



* Bachelor or Master degree;
* \\+8 years of development experience and strong knowledge of RPA (Automation Anywhere), finance and accounting systems/ functionalities and integration methodologies;
* Deep understanding of leading RPA platforms (Automation Anywhere \\& Power Automate) is a must;
* Proficiency in advanced RPA development techniques, including complex workflows, exception handling, and error management;
* Knowledge of platform architecture, infrastructure requirements, and scalability;
* Excellent knowledge of integrating RPA tools with databases, Open AI components, Applications like SAP and other COTS product is a must;
* Experience in developing large\\-scale applications in finance and accounting domains is necessary;
* Strong understanding of programming concepts and languages;
* Knowledge of cloud\\-based RPA deployments and management;
* Experience in identifying automation opportunities and assessing their feasibility;
* Experience in creating technical design documents and architecture diagrams;
* Ability to evaluate and select appropriate RPA tools and technologies;
* Knowledge of security and compliance requirements;
* Fluent in English;
